{
  "stem": "10644.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was permitted to take-- because of my publications of my previous studies in Munich, I was-- didn't have to go as a resident, just simply to take the examinations.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in 1960 I protracted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in 1960 I became a diplomat, American-style.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long-- how long did you practice obstetrics and gynecology in New York?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until what year?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] life, I was in New York-- all [? the ?] life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is from '53 to '70-- to '80.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if I were to ask you now, how many babies did you personally deliver?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately, I told you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Approximately, it must be-- it stretches-- stretches around 40 years or 50 years of practice, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I counted [INAUDIBLE] approximately it should be around 7,000.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mine-- I delivered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was-- in [INAUDIBLE], I was the director.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was before head of obstetrics for a year in the hospital, University Hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I delivered there Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maternity ?] [? duty ?] other, you know-- it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Over 3,000 under my supervision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am the responsible person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, you know, together it would be around 20,000 under my supervision.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[? why am I ?] [? attached? ?] You know, I see this baby for, basically, a delivery, maybe one day later on, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, proud?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very good specialty until malpractice started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The most vulnerable specialty, which became in danger, very much, it was obstetrics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, you know, that in the 15th, 16th, 17th century, a woman gave birth to an abnormal child, and if the husband wanted to get rid of her, he would say she had relations with the devil.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She would be burned at stake.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
